text: Bjarkey Gunnarsdóttir is an Icelandic politician. She has served as a member of the Parliament of Iceland since 2013, representing the North East ==References== Category:Living people Category:1965 births Bjarkey Gunnarsdottir Bjarkey Gunnarsdottir Bjarkey Gunnarsdottir Bjarkey Gunnarsdottir
